It’s the first time in a long time that I have not been with @christopherspitzmiller to celebrate his 🎂! So many fun ones to remember and great memories in between! Here’s to many, many more!  Happy Birthday!  We ♥️ you Uncle Chris!  Xx

Breaking news….Turning the page to a new chapter!  After almost 20 years in the design industry in New York City, I am thrilled to announce that I will now be living and working in Millbrook, NY full time, selling real estate in the stunning Hudson Valley with @hudsonvalleyatcompass. 
 
The design world has been good to me, and it has been a fabulous run!  I thank my project managers, clients and vendors for making it a joy to come to work every day.  My dream has become a reality.  A top selling monograph, countless projects from coast to coast and unending support from the media and friends…but now it’s time to dream again. 
 
I will continue as the creative director on our exciting final projects and my enormously talented Studio Director Alex Wilson will take over day to day operations at AWD.  I am delighted that Alex will start his own firm, @alexander_d_wilson, in the new year. Alex has been a designer and leader on my team for almost ten years.  He brings imagination, integrity and ingenuity to everything he does.  I can’t wait to see his star shine even brighter! 
 
In the meantime, I am very much looking forward to spending more time in the beautiful home and life that I have created in Millbrook and I hope you will join me in exploring the incredible Hudson Valley.  Let’s find the home of YOUR dreams together! 
 
It is going to be another fun ride!  Xx, Ashley. 📷 @melanieacevedophoto
